Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.38,1:36:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(莫克斯利药房)
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.69,1:37:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a good job, FBI agent?\N当联邦密探很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.03,1:37:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to travel around and stuff?\N要经常出门的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.99,1:37:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, better places than this?\N我是说，去比这里好的地方？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.87,1:37:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you do.\N有时要的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.37,1:37:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Freddie was so happy for me when I got this job at the bank.\N我找到这份银行工作时，弗瑞德瑞卡很替我高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.88,1:37:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Toaster giveaways and Barry Manilow on the speakers all day.\N有烤面包机赠品，还有整天播着巴瑞·曼尼罗的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.88,1:37:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought it was such hot shit.\N她觉得这是份好差事
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.93,1:37:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she know? Big dummy.\N她知道什么？大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.43,1:37:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy, did Fredrica ever mention a man...\N斯黛西，弗瑞德瑞卡有没有提过一个……
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.76,1:37:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,named Jamie Gumb or a Jame Gumb?\N叫杰米·冈姆布的男人？或者詹姆·冈姆布的人？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.71,1:37:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.23,1:37:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How about John Grant?\N约翰·格兰特呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.64,1:37:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\N没有
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.73,1:37:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would she have had a friend that you didn't know about, or...\N她有没有一个你不认识的朋友，或……？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.11,1:37:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. If she had a guy, I'd have known, believe me.\N不可能，如果她有男朋友，我一定会知道
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.03,1:37:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sewing was her life.\N缝纫是她的命根
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.36,1:37:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you two ever work together?\N你们曾一起工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.28,1:37:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure. Me and Pam Malavesi used...\N哦，是的，我和潘·玛拉维西曾帮她……
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.07,1:37:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to help her do alterations for old Mrs. Lippman.\N一起做利普曼太太的替工
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.37,1:37:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me Mrs. Lippman's address?\N可以把她的地址给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.91,1:37:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to her.\N我要跟她谈谈
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.40,1:37:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,(伊利诺斯州卡柳梅特城)
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.17,1:38:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,(INSECTS BUZZING)
