Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.26,1:38:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You get me a telephone and lower it down here. Now!\N不！你立刻给我吊个电话下来！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.52,1:38:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Poolie-poo. Precious.\N乖乖，珍宝？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.19,1:38:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling heart, are you all right?\N亲爱的宝贝，你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.94,1:39:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a lot of pain, mister.\N她很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.57,1:39:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs a vet.\N她需要找兽医
