Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.16,1:39:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you hurt my dog!\N你敢伤害我的狗！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.29,1:39:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you make me hurt your dog!\N你别逼我伤害你的狗！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.37,1:39:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't know what pain is!\N你不知道什么是痛楚！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.92,1:39:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me a live telephone line down here or the dog's dead!\N给我拿电话来，否则我杀死它！
