Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.22,1:39:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,CATHERINE: Get me that telephone!\N你还是给我拿电话来！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.68,1:39:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do it, mister!\N我要动手了，先生！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.89,1:39:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll snap her neck off. I swear to God!\N我会折断它的颈，我发誓我会的！
