Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.77,1:40:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon. Sorry to bother you.\N午安，抱歉打扰你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.31,1:40:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm looking for Mrs. Lippman's family.\N我在……我在找利普曼太太的家人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.19,1:40:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI! Everybody down!\N联邦调查局！所有人趴下！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.40,1:40:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody down, now!\N所有人趴下！马上！
