Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.90,1:40:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Excuse me, sir.\N对不起，先生
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.36,1:40:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I really need to speak with you.\N我真的需要跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.74,1:40:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Clear!\N- Clear!\N- 没有人！\N- 没有人！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.58,1:40:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,(STUTTERING) What's the problem, Officer?\N有什么问题呢，警官？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.91,1:40:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm investigating the death of Fredrica Bimmel.\N我正在调查弗瑞德瑞卡·比默尔的死因
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.08,1:40:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here, Jack.\N这里一个人也没有，杰克
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.09,1:40:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarice.\N克拉丽丝
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.59,1:40:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is?\N阁下是……
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.88,1:40:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jack Gordon.\N杰克·戈登
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.38,1:40:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gordon. Good. Um...\N戈登先生，很好，嗯……
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.34,1:40:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Fredrica used to work for Mrs. Lippman.\N弗瑞德瑞卡是利普曼太太的雇员
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.47,1:40:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know her?\N你认识她吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.56,1:40:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Uh-uh.\N不认识
