Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.52,1:41:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she a great, big fat person?\N她是不是身材肥胖？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.65,1:41:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She was a big girl, sir.\N是，她很肥胖
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.44,1:41:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I...\N对，我……
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.69,1:41:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have...\N我可能有……
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.78,1:41:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I read about her in the newspaper.\N不，我是在报纸上读到她的新闻
