Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.53,1:41:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Lippman had a son. Maybe he could help you.\N利普曼太太有个儿子，他或许可以帮忙
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.07,1:41:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I got his card in here someplace.\N我这里有他的名片
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.91,1:41:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come in while I look for it?\N在我找他名片的时候你要进来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.49,1:41:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- May I?\N- Yeah, sure.\N- 可以吗？\N- 当然可以
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.79,1:41:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.81,1:41:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you close to catching somebody, you think?\N你觉得你们快抓到人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.48,1:41:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We may be.\N是的，或者吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.86,1:41:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you...\N你是不是……
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.03,1:41:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,take over this place after Mrs. Lippman died? Is that right?\N在利普曼太太死后搬到这里来？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.95,1:41:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I bought this house, uh, two years ago.\N是的，我两年前买了这间屋
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.49,1:42:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she leave any records, any business records,\N她有没有留下任何记录，任何业务记录……
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.08,1:42:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,tax forms, list of employees?\N税单、雇员名单之类？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.38,1:42:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing like that at all.\N没有，完全没有
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.84,1:42:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, has the FBI learned something?\N联邦调查局有什么发现吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.76,1:42:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The police around here don't seem to have the first clue.\N这里的警方看来毫无头绪
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.65,1:42:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, have you got, like, a description, fingerprints,\N我是说，你们有没有获得相貌、指纹……
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.19,1:42:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,anything like that?\N之类的线索？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.70,1:42:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\N没有
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.53,1:42:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't.\N我们没有
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.54,1:42:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Here's that number.\N对，是这个电话号码了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.21,1:42:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, Mr. Gordon.\N很好，戈登先生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.05,1:42:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,May I use your phone, please?\N可不可以借用你的电话？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.14,1:43:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you can use my phone.\N当然可以
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.40,1:43:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!\N别动！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.57,1:43:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands over your head!\N把双手放在头上！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.40,1:43:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And turn around! Spread your legs!\N转过来！张开腿！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.74,1:43:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread your legs!\N张开腿！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.41,1:43:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands in the back! Thumbs up!\N把双手放在……
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.28,1:43:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!\N别动！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.33,1:44:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,(BREATHING HEAVILY)
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.80,1:44:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,(PRECIOUS BARKING)
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.31,1:44:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,CATHERINE: Hey!\N喂！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.95,1:44:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(MUSIC PLAYING)
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.84,1:44:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,CATHERINE: Hello! Are you there?\N喂！你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.92,1:45:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm down here! I'm down here!\N我在下面！我在下面！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.35,1:45:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,(PRECIOUS BARKING)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.36,1:45:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Catherine Martin?\N凯瑟琳·马丁？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.78,1:45:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,CATHERINE: Yes!\N是！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.20,1:45:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI! You're safe!\N联邦调查局！你安全了！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.20,1:45:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe, shit! Get me out of here!\N安全个屁！快救我出去
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.17,1:45:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(GRUNTS)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.22,1:45:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right, Catherine. Where is he?\N你没事的，凯瑟琳。他在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.39,1:45:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How the fuck should I know?\N我他妈的怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.98,1:45:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get me out of here!\N快救我出去！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.48,1:45:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Catherine, you've got to be quiet. Now shut that dog up!\N凯瑟琳，你静一点，叫那只狗别吵！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.69,1:45:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get me out of here!\N快救我出去！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.90,1:45:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.\N我的天
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.70,1:46:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Catherine, I'm going to get you out of there,\N凯瑟琳，我会救你出来的……
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.24,1:46:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but right now, you listen to me.\N但现在你要听我说
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.91,1:46:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to leave this room. I'll be right back.\N我得离开这个房间，我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.33,1:46:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't you leave me here, you fucking bitch!\N不！不要丢下我，你这个婊子！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.25,1:46:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't you leave me here!\N不！不要丢下我！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.96,1:46:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's fucking crazy!\N这个家伙是疯子！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.13,1:46:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!\N等一下！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.84,1:46:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get out of here!\N我得离开这里！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.21,1:46:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!\N求求你！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.60,1:46:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Catherine, the other officers will be here any minute now!\N凯瑟琳！其他的探员会很快到达的！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.56,1:46:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!\N不要走！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.44,1:46:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go! Please!\N不要走！求求你！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.40,1:46:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,CLARICE: Quiet!\N别吵！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.11,1:46:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God!\N天啊……
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.46,1:50:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,(恐怖)
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.23,1:50:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,(比尔剥下第五个人的皮)
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.70,1:50:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(OFFICER CHATTERING ON RADIO)
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.55,1:50:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?\N你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.81,1:50:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gunpowder. It's nothing. I'm okay.\N- Agent Starling,\N- 枪震，不要紧，我没事\N- 斯达琳探员……
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.74,1:50:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how did you track Buffalo Bill to this address?\N你怎么追查到水牛比尔在这里的？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.60,1:50:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,(PEOPLE APPLAUDING)\N(司法部联邦调查局)
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.36,1:50:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarice M. Starling.\N克拉丽丝·M.斯达琳
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.36,1:50:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.\N恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.21,1:51:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ernest W. Stevens.\N厄内斯特·W.斯蒂文斯
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.17,1:51:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,(PEOPLE APPLAUDING)
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.02,1:51:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,(PEOPLE CHATTERING)
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.02,1:51:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Agent Starling!\N特别探员克拉丽丝·斯达琳！
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.69,1:51:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Special Agent Mapp.\N哦，特别探员麦普
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.24,1:51:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Phone call.\N- Thank you.\N- 有电话找你\N- 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.90,1:51:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, gentlemen.\N失陪，先生们
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.07,1:51:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Starling.\N斯达琳
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.99,1:51:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilch, could you take our picture?\N皮尔奇，能替我们拍张照吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.00,1:51:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.\N好的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.58,1:51:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I just wanted to say congratulations.\N我只想说声恭喜
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.79,1:51:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not much good at this kind of thing,\N我不擅应酬这类事……
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.84,1:51:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm gonna duck out of here.\N所以我要走了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.63,1:51:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure.\N好的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.63,1:51:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Crawford.\N谢谢，克劳福德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.43,1:52:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father would have been proud today.\N令尊今天一定会很骄傲
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.86,1:52:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your phone call.\N别忘了接听电话
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.28,1:52:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Starling.\N斯达琳
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.78,1:52:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Clarice, have the lambs stopped screaming?\N那么，克拉丽丝，那些羔羊停止尖叫了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.87,1:52:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Lecter.\N莱克特医生？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.29,1:52:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother with a trace. I won't be on long enough.\N不必追踪这个电话，我不会说太久
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.84,1:52:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Dr. Lecter?\N莱克特医生，你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.84,1:52:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no plans to call on you, Clarice.\N我不打算找你了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.13,1:52:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's more interesting with you in it.\N有了你，这个世界更加有趣
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.18,1:52:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you take care now to extend me the same courtesy.\N所以你多保重，日后报答我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.43,1:52:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't make that promise.\N你知道我不能做那个承诺的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.43,1:52:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I do wish we could chat longer,\N但愿我们可以多聊一会……
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.14,1:52:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm having an old friend for dinner.\N但我有个老朋友要一起吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.27,1:52:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.\N再见
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.98,1:52:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Lecter!\N莱克特医生！
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.74,1:52:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Lecter.\N莱克特医生
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.54,1:53:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Lecter.\N莱克特医生
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.64,1:53:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Lecter?\N莱克特医生？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.83,1:53:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what? Oh, excuse me. I'm sorry.\N嘿，什么？抱歉，对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.25,1:53:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the security system all set up?\N保安系统安排好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.79,1:53:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the big-shot security.\N我们有严密保安的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.29,1:53:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I appreciate that.\N谢谢，我很感谢
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.84,1:53:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(PEOPLE CHATTERING)
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.64,1:53:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(MAN SINGING)
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.42,1:58:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(谨以本片献给崔·威尔森)

